channel.description:
Most Popular Boards By Activity [b]SRL Public Scripts 50.0000%[/b]

item.dc:creator: @exe626 exe626
item.description:
@exe626 wrote:

…Mmm. I’m pretty positive I joined this website a few weeks before my moms birthday. I was scanning the web for a website in which I could learn the basics of Java. Guess what? This was the 4th listed at the time. I was a bit skeptical at the time seeing ‘Mopar’ but I decided to look around, finding some things interesting, so I joined. After a few months of learning, I started posting scarcely in some off-topic areas, worked my way to ‘Moparscape’ because I Was told they where programming different games. I soon found out they hadn’t a single idea of what they where talking about, so I migrated back here.
